foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although VA indicated in its FY2011 Annual lReport that there were 1,425 requests pending at the end of the fiscal year, the figure denoted in this chart is correct. The difference is attributed to the following: 1) in some instances the office did not show requests that were in fact completed in FY 2011 as completed in VA's FOIA tracking system until after the FY2011 report was finalized, and 2) there were some discrepancies in accounting.

foia:BackloggedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: Although VA indicated in its FY2011 Annual Report that there were 794 requests backlogged at the end of the fiscal year, the figure denoted in this chart is correct. The difference is attributed to the following: 1) in some instances the office did noot show requests that were in fact backlogged in Fy2011 as completed in VA's FOiA tracking system until after the FY2011 report was finalized, and 2) there were some discrepancies in accounting.
